.archive.org/web/20200204123549/https://www.theverge.com/2020/2/3/21120531/disney-plus-hamilton-streaming-theaters-distribution-broadway |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影將采用與2016年在{{link-en|理查德·羅傑斯劇院|Richard Rodgers Theatre}}演出時的錄像。

